# API Documentation Standards

All HTTP Handler methods must include complete Swagger annotations.

## Full Annotation Example

```go
// ListArticles retrieves a paginated list of articles.
// @Summary List articles
// @Description Paginated article list with optional status filtering
// @Tags article
// @Accept json
// @Produce json
// @Param status query string false "Article status" Enums(draft, published, archived)
// @Param limit query int false "Page size" default(20) minimum(1) maximum(100)
// @Param page query int false "Page number" default(1) minimum(1)
// @Success 200 {object} dto.ListArticlesResponse
// @Failure 400 {object} utils.AppError
// @Failure 401 {object} utils.AppError
// @Failure 500 {object} utils.AppError
// @Router /api/articles [get]
func (h *ArticleHandler) ListArticles(c *gin.Context) {
    // ...
}
```

## Required Annotations

| Annotation | Description | Example |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `@Summary` | Short description | `List articles` |
| `@Tags` | API group | `article` |
| `@Accept` | Request format | `json` |
| `@Produce` | Response format | `json` |
| `@Router` | Route path and method | `/api/articles [get]` |
| `@Success` | Success response | `200 {object} dto.Response` |

## Parameter Annotations

### Query Parameters

```go
// @Param name query string false "Parameter description"
// @Param limit query int false "Page size" default(20) minimum(1) maximum(100)
// @Param status query string false "Status" Enums(active, inactive)
```

### Path Parameters

```go
// @Param id path string true "Article ID"
// @Router /api/articles/{id} [get]
```

### Header Parameters

```go
// @Param Authorization header string true "Bearer token"
```

### Body Parameters

```go
// @Param request body dto.CreateArticleRequest true "Create article request"
```

## Response Annotations

```go
// Success response
// @Success 200 {object} dto.ArticleResponse
// @Success 201 {object} dto.ArticleResponse

// Error responses
// @Failure 400 {object} utils.AppError "Bad request"
// @Failure 401 {object} utils.AppError "Unauthorized"
// @Failure 403 {object} utils.AppError "Forbidden"
// @Failure 404 {object} utils.AppError "Not found"
// @Failure 500 {object} utils.AppError "Internal server error"
```

## Tags Grouping

Each domain module uses its own Tag. Add new entries when adding modules:

| Tag | Domain |
| :--- | :--- |
| `Auth` | Authentication (login, registration) |
| `User` | User management |
| `health` | Health check |

## DTO Annotations

```go
// ListArticlesResponse is the article list response.
type ListArticlesResponse struct {
    // Article list
    Articles []*ArticleInfo `json:"articles"`
    // Total count
    TotalCount int `json:"total_count"`
}

// ArticleInfo contains article information.
type ArticleInfo struct {
    // Article ID
    ID string `json:"id" example:"article-123456"`
    // Article title
    Title string `json:"title" example:"My First Post"`
    // Article status
    Status string `json:"status" example:"published" enums:"draft,published,archived"`
}
```

## Generate Documentation

```bash
# Generate Swagger documentation
make doc

# Output goes to cmd/api/docs/
# - docs.go
# - swagger.json
# - swagger.yaml
```

## Access Documentation

- Swagger UI: `http://localhost:8000/swagger/index.html`
- API JSON: `http://localhost:8000/swagger/doc.json`

